summary: Whitepaper - $DOEGE Coin is a community-driven cryptocurrency born out of the collective love for a drooly, dumb and silly DOGE named DOEGE. Launched in 2024, with a total supply of 1 billion tokens, DOEGE Coin aims to capture the essence of internet culture and meme-driven communities. Through memes and a shared affection for DOEGE, our community seeks to spread joy and build connections among cryptocurrency enthusiasts and meme lovers worldwide.
